\subsection{Level 5: LLM-as-a-Judge Evaluation}

A stratified sample of 250 couplets was evaluated by Gemini~3~Pro (Vertex AI
Batch API) using a five-dimensional rubric (1--5 scale) based on
G-Eval~\citep{liu2023geval} and GEMBA~\citep{kocmi2023gemba}. Dimensions
cover: (1) semantic fidelity, (2) completeness, (3) cultural and contextual
accuracy, (4) Telugu linguistic quality, and (5) English linguistic quality.
Table~\ref{tab:llmjudge} reports dimension-level results.

